Belgian thriller series. Quarantine has been prolonged and certain food products are starting to become scarce. Lex starts organising food distribution via the container sluices.

Quarantine has been prolonged and certain food products are starting to become scarce within the cordon. Lex starts organising food distribution via the container sluices. Leo has asked his friend Ingrid to provide a video diary from within the cordon, but soon realises the enormity of the tradegy unfolding when Ingrid films the death of her own girlfriend struck by the lethal virus.
